<h5>3.  Platform Fee, Ad Success, Optimized Success & Hosting Fees for Use of the Platform.</h5>

                <ul>
                    <li>3.1	Platform Fee. Beginning on the Effective Date, you agree to pay Adap.tv a monthly Platform Fee of $495 per month.</li>
                    <li>3.2	Ad Success Fee.  You agree to pay Adap.tv a cost per thousand (CPM) of twelve cents ($0.12) per Ad Success. <strong>"Ad Success"</strong> is defined as the number of times Prioritized or Committed Ads are delivered by the Platform for display on the Partner Site(s), as counted by Adap.tv using a methodology that is substantially similar with industry standards.</li>
                    <li>3.3	Ad Optimization Fee and Inventory Optimization Fee.  You agree to pay Adap.tv twelve percent (12%) of the total gross revenues generated by all Optimized Ad Successes and all Optimized Inventory Successes. <strong>"Optimized Ad Success"</strong> is defined as the ability to place and display the highest paying Ad or Ad sources, via the Platform's Optimized Ad management setup. <strong>"Optimized Inventory Success"</strong> is defined as the ability to pick inventory for the display of Ads that meet the specific criteria you select, via the Platform's trafficking management setup.
</li>
                    <li>3.4	Ad Hosting Fee. You agree to pay Adap.tv a fee for Ad hosting and streaming provided by the Platform (the <strong>"Ad Hosting Fee(s)"</strong>). The Ad Hosting Fee is a cost per thousand (CPM) of fifteen cents ($0.15) per gigabyte of streamed content that is hosted by Adap.tv, as measured by Adap.tv. Alternatively, you may host and stream Ads by your own means or using a third-party service of your choice; and in such an event, you will not owe the Ad Hosting Fee.</li>
                    <li>3.5	Payment Terms. Adap.tv will calculate and report to you after the end of such calendar month all applicable Ad Successes, Optimized Ad Successes and Optimized Inventory Successes in such month and will invoice you the combined amount of all such fees.  Adap.tv's invoice will be due and payable by you within thirty (30) days from your receipt of such invoice. All payments shall be made in U.S. dollars. Payments will be calculated solely based on records maintained by Adap.tv.</li>
                    <li>3.6	Taxes. Adap.tv assumes no responsibility for paying income taxes on your behalf. You assume complete and sole responsibility for any taxes owed as a consequence of your activities under the Agreement, and agree to indemnify and hold Adap.tv and its employees, affiliates and representatives harmless from any such taxes. Adap.tv shall provide you with appropriate tax information, including earnings on Form 1099 as required by applicable law. If you reside in the United States, then you agree to provide your Social Security number or Federal Employee Identification Number and any other reasonable information to Adap.tv for tax reporting purposes. Such information will be used for no purpose other than for tax reporting purposes. If you reside outside of the United States, then you may be asked to complete appropriate forms for tax purposes, and you agree to accurately complete such forms. Adap.tv may withhold payment from you in the event you do not provide accurate tax information or complete any necessary tax or reporting forms, as determined in Adap.tv's reasonable discretion.</li>

